    "chunk_id": "mineru_newspaper_4b4ad1f6cba28a4844d7ffa9306223a4_1_0",
    "text": "三部门再次公布举报电话 严查虚假报道",
    "canon_role": "section_header",
    "bbox": [
      0.017429193899782137,
